{"tid":472344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德軍火商拒絕售武予香港警察","createTime":"2017-11-18T06:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T06:58:58.000Z","uid":54785,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20c19d7cfeb6eb8a4ca4db5dd571cfa2e15f33ab","tid":472344,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"據悉，香港警方的MP5槍械由德國Heckler &amp; Koch（H&amp;K）供應，H&amp;K是全球最大型槍械公司之一。民權觀察16日晚上在Facebook專頁發文指出，英國報章《獨立報》去年底曾經報道，H&amp;K不會再將武器輸出到不民主及腐敗的地區或國家（原文為 &quot;no longer supply undemocratic, corrupt countries&quot;），因為與這些地區交易，難以向政府取得出口許可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171116/57467447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57467447&d=iXPG7n%2BZlQYRPUdsVi1iJp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d2e5db24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57467447&h=6334ac9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171116/57467447</a><br />\n<br />\nIn November last year, a report from German news agency DPA cited an unnamed manager of Heckler &amp; Koch as saying: &ldquo;We only want to deliver to solid countries &ndash; that means unequivocally democratic, definitely not corrupt, and in NATO or close to NATO.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2017/11/17/german-firm-refuses-sell-submachine-guns-hong-kong-police-force-lawmaker-blames-decline-human-rights/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2Fgerman-firm-refuses-sell-submachine-guns-hong-kong-police-force-lawmaker-blames-decline-human-rights%2F&d=iXPG7n%2BZlQYRPUdsVi1iJp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7ef2f9fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2017/11/17/german-firm-refuses-sell-submachine-guns-hong-kong-police-force-lawmaker-blames-decline-human-rights/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691f30a0e13099cd766ac0ecf0e2e194783b8425","tid":472344,"uid":89134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"8a77d0ed6f3d2bf22fddf982d1126b8c6113448e","tid":472344,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3964eb560e9832fad964cfef9d62fcc3241f07","tid":472344,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f783acc8b72f524c1553efbdff337e316d85c7","tid":472344,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n